title: Seoul Food DC
typeOfFood: Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Fusion, Korean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Korean fusion food truck turned brick and mortar. Some dishes come with choice of tofu, and staff can offers suggestions or ask the kitchen to make a dish vegan. Try the caramelized tofu in bibimbap, a vegan version of the Korean fusion burrito or bowl.
